  "min_marlin": "2.0.0",
  "note": "Creality V1.1.2 through V1.1.5 are 8-bit Melzi-derived ATmega1284P boards. Select A4988 for standard/non-silent boards and TMC2208_STANDALONE for V1.1.4/V1.1.5 silent-driver variants after verifying the installed driver hardware. Firmware is exported as Intel HEX and flashed over USB serial or ISP; these boards do not update Marlin from an SD card.",
  "wifi": {
